lead_paragraph: Everton manager Roberto Martinez conceded he is worried with his team's poor home form after the Toffees slumped to their fifth loss at Goodison Park this campaign in Sunday's 2-1 Premier League defeat by Swansea City.

headline.print_headline: Everton's Poor Home Form Worries Martinez
